    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. It is equipped with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure timing precision. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers that maintain the original suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with road use, the drivetrain remains robust with excellent compression. A mechanically sound example of a modern classic, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
